				    label      	
|This diagram shows all the analysis classes with high-level attributes, as they are captured during the early analysis work.
|
|Some of these classes will evolve one-to-one into design classes, others are replaced by complete subsystems, yet others may be discarded as we move into design.
|
|This part of the model is considered temporary.
